Standardize maxquant snames

standardize_maxquant_snames.Rd

Standardize maxquant sample names

standardize_maxquant_snames(x, ...)

# S3 method for character
standardize_maxquant_snames(
  x,
  quantity = guess_maxquant_quantity(x),
  verbose = FALSE,
  ...
)

# S3 method for SummarizedExperiment
standardize_maxquant_snames(
  x,
  quantity = guess_maxquant_quantity(x),
  verbose = FALSE,
  ...
)

Arguments

x

character vector or SummarizedExperiment
...

allow for proper S3 method dispatch
quantity

maxquant quantity
verbose

TRUE (default) or FALSE

Value

character vector or SummarizedExperiment

Details

Drop "Ratio normalized", "LFQ intensity" etc from maxquant sample names

Examples

# character vector
   x <- "Ratio M/L normalized STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1"
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1{M/L}"

   x <- "Ratio M/L STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1"
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1{M/L}"

   x <-'LFQ intensity STD_R1'
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "STD_R1"

   x <- 'LFQ intensity L STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1'
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "STD(L)_EM00(M)_EM01(H)_R1{L}"

   x <-'Reporter intensity 0 A(0)_B(1)_C(2)_D(3)_E(4)_F(5)_R1'
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "A(0)_B(1)_C(2)_D(3)_E(4)_F(5)_R1{0}"

   x <- 'Reporter intensity corrected 0 A(0)_B(1)_C(2)_D(3)_E(4)_F(5)_R1'
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> [1] "A(0)_B(1)_C(2)_D(3)_E(4)_F(5)_R1{0}"

# SummarizedExperiment
   file <- download_data('stemcells.proteinGroups.txt')

#> Use already available file: ~/importomicscache/datasets/stemcells/stemcells.proteinGroups.txt
   x <- read_proteingroups(file, demultiplex_snames = FALSE)

#> 	Filter features
#> 		Retain 8528/8627 features: ~Reverse != "+"
#> 		Retain 8408/8528 features: contaminant != '+'
#> 		Retain 7877/8408 features: non-zero, non-NA, and non-NaN for some sample
#> 		Guess subgroup values from sampleids: Ratio M/L normalized E(L).EM(M).BM(H).R1 => Ratio M/L normalized E(L).EM(M).BM(H)
#> 	Transform exprs
#> 		Replace NaN -> NA for 6935/70893 values (in 1565/7877 features and 9/9 samples)
#> 		Log2 transform exprs
   standardize_maxquant_snames(x)

#> class: SummarizedExperiment
